descriptionHtml:
This is my first attempt at a Racemenu preset. This is just a wood elf. Not an odd race or anything. The idea was a plant based elf so I made her green with purple hair trying to make her resemble a flower. Even her name is based on a purple daylilly. I know this isn't lore friendly in the least but I'd rather use my imagination than rigid self imposed rules and stipulations.

You will need

Brows: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?

and

Ponytail Hairstyles v3_0: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31797/?

Both of which are great mods.

For the body I use UNPB so i don't know how it will turn out with other bodies so let me know.
 
Please keep in mind I play Skyrim on a laptop so I have my graphics set to medium so not the best screenshots in the world. I would love to see how she looks on a better rig so feel free to post/send pics.
author: GrimKusanagi
